import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import {createRouter, createWebHistory} from 'vue-router'
import TheSchedule from '../src/components/page/TheSchedule.vue'

const routers = [
    {path: "/schedule", component: TheSchedule},
    {path: "/mission", component: TheSchedule},
    {path: "/transport", component: OverView},
    {path: "/advance", component: OverView},
    {path: "/pay", component: StaffList},
    {path: "/establish", component: StaffList},
]

const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes: routers,
})

const app = createApp(App);

app.use(router).mount('#app')
